toffeed.title: Toffeed - A Facebook mobile web wrapper
toffeed.lead: As a small project for my small summer break, I developed a wrapper app for Facebook. It simply encloses the Facebook’s mobile website in a WebView and uses JavaScript Interfaces to obtain data from the pages.

moved-to-jekyll.title: Moved to Jekyll!
moved-to-jekyll.lead: I’ve converted my static site into a Jekyll generated one so I can have a blog.
